  <span property="dc:title" content="Hongkongers must learn some self-control when shopping for clothes" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span><span property="sioc:num_replies" content="12" datatype="xsd:integer" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span><div class="non-annotated-image">
  <a href="/comment/insight-opinion/article/2065651/hongkongers-must-learn-some-self-control-when-shopping"><img typeof="foaf:Image" data-original="http://cdn3.i-scmp.com/sites/default/files/styles/220x137/public/images/methode/2017/01/27/7a4bbdca-e377-11e6-8801-9f557f980a64_image_hires.JPG?itok=0w8DB9V3&amp;v=1485488639" width="220" height="137" alt="Huge signs advertise discounts at a Causeway Bay store on January 2. Promises of bargains are often hard to resist, with so much advertising in our faces and shops everywhere. Photo: Felix Wong" title="Huge signs advertise discounts at a Causeway Bay store on January 2. Promises of bargains are often hard to resist, with so much advertising in our faces and shops everywhere. Photo: Felix Wong" class="lazyload-processed loaded" src="http://cdn3.i-scmp.com/sites/default/files/styles/220x137/public/images/methode/2017/01/27/7a4bbdca-e377-11e6-8801-9f557f980a64_image_hires.JPG?itok=0w8DB9V3&amp;v=1485488639" data-ignore="true"></a></div><div class="content-wrapper">
